<?php
// Given string
$text = "PHP is powerful. Learning PHP is fun. PHP is widely used.";

// Word to count
$word = "PHP";

// Use substr_count() to count the number of times the word appears
$count = substr_count($text, $word);

// Display result
echo "The word '$word' occurs $count times in the given string.";
?>


OUTPUT:

The word 'PHP' occurs 3 times in the given string.
